data.title: Maria-Laetizia Ramolino Bonaparte, Madame Mère (ca. 1750-1836) Lithograph by L. Dupré.
data.meta_description: Mother of Napoleon Bonaparte. Under the Empire, she was Protectrice Générale of charitable and welfare establishments, including hospitals
